 // SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0
 /*
- * FMan PCD Coarse Classifier (CC) - tree create/destroy.
+ * FMan PCD Coarse Classifier (CC) - tree + node create/destroy.
  *
- * PR14c-body-1 of the ASK2 v1.0 PR14 series.  Replaces the
- * PR14c-prep -EOPNOTSUPP stubs for fman_pcd_cc_tree_create() and
- * fman_pcd_cc_tree_destroy() with real MURAM-resident tree-group-
