- * stubs (fman_pcd_cc_node_create, _add_key, _modify_next_action,
- * _destroy) land in PR14c-body-2..-4.
+ * PR14c-body-2 of the ASK2 v1.0 PR14 series.  Replaces the
+ * PR14c-prep -EOPNOTSUPP stubs for fman_pcd_cc_node_create() and
+ * fman_pcd_cc_node_destroy() with real MURAM-resident match-key
+ * record + AD-table allocation per LS1046A RM 8.7.4.2 and 8.7.4.3.
+ * Tree create/destroy bodies landed in PR14c-body-1.  The remaining
+ * two stubs (fman_pcd_cc_node_add_key, _modify_next_action) land in
+ * PR14c-body-4 once the action-encoding helper from PR14c-body-3 is
